{"tid":433753,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"想彈番琴但係又唔知點練得好","createTime":"2017-10-12T15:21:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-26T04:34:22.000Z","uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"cc30f449539250d34115a85c8296184bbb29464d","tid":433753,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T15:21:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/3Ny5x-PSisc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F3Ny5x-PSisc&d=8nx%2BPB6fXn8UCiGc1HdqQiwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=b4f3c1ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/3Ny5x-PSisc</a><br />\n我都知自己垃圾嫁啦，但係妹下妹下個琴又真係無咩方向感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n條片我不求有人話我彈得正常，大家辨識到我彈咩歌就得番嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d0a7272febf561a7c0b75322f02c38a5cf1af17","tid":433753,"uid":32279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T15:30:21.000Z","msg":"最近彈番琴練梗蕭邦首英雄波蘭<br />\n搵自己鍾意既黎練咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"938a4bb378453063fe1d34a3313e0b1a7f0dcd79","tid":433753,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T15:31:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/3Ny5x-PSisc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F3Ny5x-PSisc&d=8nx%2BPB6fXn8UCiGc1HdqQiwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=b4f3c1ce\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/3Ny5x-PSisc</a><br />\n唔記得變URL<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95bdc28e192a9898fcb20d8085126fd12efae218","tid":433753,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T01:40:01.000Z","msg":"有冇高手留言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e22081efa98a3caefaddb55297efd0bd8fa4bb20","tid":433753,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T06:35:42.000Z","msg":"再推上黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢幾日我都有練但練黎練去冇咩突破咁，每日都差唔多，彈到唔好聽嘅繼續唔好聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有咩解決辦法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8f21ae3774098e8d14f22c9f2b1aa3943762d2a","tid":433753,"uid":73366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T11:22:23.000Z","msg":"自學定出面學過？練得唔熟同埋隻手彈落去個下比較硬同用力喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18bb0d1f0e0727447d37fa0f83b9414f735ebab1","tid":433753,"uid":141550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T11:30:11.000Z","msg":"聽完你幾條片<br />\n<br />\n我覺得可以慢慢練 未練熟曬咁快就用正常速度會係咁卡"},{"pid":"6b980d8be388cbd6185aa121d6933512a5b4af59","tid":433753,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T11:45:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自學定出面學過？練得唔熟同埋隻手彈落去個下比較硬同用力喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n小學至中五時跟過老師<br />\n近期係自己練"},{"pid":"69c9af0e5aa21290bec751564adfdae53080dfac","tid":433753,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T11:46:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聽完你幾條片<br />\n<br />\n我覺得可以慢慢練 未練熟曬咁快就用正常速度會係咁卡</blockquote><br />\nyes<br />\n幾條片都係搏負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為有時真係唔識點樣處理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2737db5fa3333f12be4ea3f17858805326d71438","tid":433753,"uid":141550,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T13:43:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>聽完你幾條片<br />\n<br />\n我覺得可以慢慢練 未練熟曬咁快就用正常速度會係咁卡</blockquote><br />\nyes<br />\n幾條片都係搏負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為有時真係唔識點樣處理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n試下彈慢d 熟左再彈快先拍片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b893ba405a8874971d6e9638c1dd96961cf599ef","tid":433753,"uid":73366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T03:36:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>自學定出面學過？練得唔熟同埋隻手彈落去個下比較硬同用力喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n小學至中五時跟過老師<br />\n近期係自己練</blockquote><br />\n我以前學琴係咁既，左右手先分開練，熟左先夾埋一齊，你學到幾級，照計小學到中五都應該學到6-7級起碼，sight-reading都應該唔曳架喎。"},{"pid":"038bb85b1e37bb68deebae91d0cf593bef30bcc1","tid":433753,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T04:33:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>聽完你幾條片<br />\n<br />\n我覺得可以慢慢練 未練熟曬咁快就用正常速度會係咁卡</blockquote><br />\nyes<br />\n幾條片都係搏負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為有時真係唔識點樣處理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n試下彈慢d 熟左再彈快先拍片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n拍片係求改善<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb60ab0d7138d1c9837fc54e0ff2397360718834","tid":433753,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T04:34:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>自學定出面學過？練得唔熟同埋隻手彈落去個下比較硬同用力喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n小學至中五時跟過老師<br />\n近期係自己練</blockquote><br />\n我以前學琴係咁既，左右手先分開練，熟左先夾埋一齊，你學到幾級，照計小學到中五都應該學到6-7級起碼，sight-reading都應該唔曳架喎。</blockquote><br />\n5級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我好很hea<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}